text: Jasmin Gabriela Soto López (born 11 January 1993) is a Guatemalan professional racing cyclist, who last rode for UCI Women's Team in the 2019 women's road cycling season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Guatemalan female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Cyclists at the 2019 Pan American Games
